Interface SecuredContainer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Container, FrontsNode, RDFNode, Resource, SecuredItem, SecuredRDFNode, SecuredResource
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    SecuredAlt, SecuredBag, SecuredSeq
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SecuredAltImpl, SecuredBagImpl, SecuredContainerImpl, SecuredSeqImpl

    public interface SecuredContainer
extends Container, SecuredResource
    The interface for secured Container instances. Use one of the SecuredContainer derived class Factory methods to create instances
